          <h2 id="regulations">Toronto STR Rules You Must Follow</h2>
          <p>The World Cup doesn't create any exemptions from <a href="/blog/toronto-airbnb-short-term-rental-rules-2026">Toronto's existing STR regulations</a>. Here's the checklist:</p>

