            <li><strong>Gen Z travelers</strong> represent over 15% of Canadian bookings, with nearly half traveling in groups</li>
            <li>Top source countries: <strong>United States, United Kingdom, and Canada</strong></li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Stay Patterns</h3>
