              <li><strong>Transit access:</strong> Highlight proximity to BMO Field, TTC stations, or the Fan Festival at Fort York</li>
              <li><strong>International guests:</strong> Make sure your listing description mentions nearby restaurants, grocery stores, and transit in clear English</li>
